\c 44
\p
\v 1 "Asi zvino chinzwa, iwe Jakobho, muranda wangu, naIsiraeri wandakasanangura,
\v 2 zvanzi naJehovha, akakuita, akakuumba kubvira pachizvaro, achakubatsira, `Usatya hako, iwe Jakobho, muranda wangu, newe Jeshuruni, wandakasanangura.
\v 3 Nokuti ndichadira mvura pamusoro penyika ine nyota, nenzizi pamusoro pevhu rakaoma; ndichadira Mweya wangu pamusoro porudzi rwako, nokuropafadza kwangu pamusoro pavana vako;
\v 4 vachamera pakati pouswa, semikonachando pamvura inoyerera.'
\p
\v 5 "Mumwe achati, `Ndiri waJehovha,' mumwezve achazvitumidza nezita raJakobho, mumwezve achanyora noruoko rwake, achiti, `Ndiri waJehovha, nokutora zita raIsiraeri.' "
\s Jehovha ndiye Mwari mumwe, zvifananidzo hazvina maturo
\p
\v 6 Zvanzi naJehovha, Mwari wavaIsiraeri, noMudzikinuri wavo, Jehovha wehondo, "Ndini wokutanga nowokupedzisira; kunze kwangu hakuna Mwari.
\v 7 Ndianiko angadana seni, nokuzviparidza, nokuzvigadzirira izvo, kubva panguva yandakagadza vanhu vakare-kare? Zvinhu zvinouya, nezvinozoitika, ngavazviparidze izvo.
\v 8 Musatya henyu, musavhunduka; handina kukuparidzirai izvozvo kare, nokukuratidzai here? Imi muri zvapupu zvangu. Kunomumwe Mwari kunze kwangu here? Zvirokwazvo, hakune rimwe dombo, ini handirizivi."
\p
\v 9 Vose vanoita mifananidzo yakavezwa havana maturo, zvinhu zvavanofarira hazvibatsiri; zvapupu zvavo hazvioni uye hazvizivi, kuti vanyadziswe.
\v 10 Ndianiko akaita mwari, kana mufananidzo wakaumbwa, zvisingabatsiri chinhu?
\p
\v 11 Tarirai, vose vanomunamatira vachanyadziswa; vakazviita, vanhu havo, ngavaunganidzwe pamwechete, ngavasimuke; vachatya, vachanyadziswa pamwechete.
\v 12 Mupfuri anopfura sanhu, anobata namazimbe, nokuriita nenyundo, nolcuripfura noruoko rune simba; zvirokwazvo ane nzara, simba rake rinopera, haanwi mvura, ndokuziya.
\v 13 Muvezi anotambanudza rwonzi, anotara mufananidzo nepenzura, ariouttatsa uembezo , fawAtzn, x‘echienzaniso, ndokuuveza zvakafanana nomunhu, zvakaenzana nomunhu akanaka, kuti ugare mumba.
\v 14 Zvino anozvitemera misidhari, ndokutora misipiresi nemiouki, achizvisanangurira mumwe pakati pemiti pamusoro pavanakomana vangu, napamusoro pebasa ramaoko angu, mundirayire.
\v 12 Ndakaita nyika, nokusika vanhu pamusoro payo; ini namaoko angu, ndakatatanura denga rose; ndakarayira hondo yose yaro.
\v 13 Ndakamumutsa nokururama, ndicharuramisa nzira dzake dzose; iye achavaka guta rangu, nokusunungura vatapwa vangu, asingatsvaki mutengo kana mubayiro," ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo.
\p
\v 14 Zvanzi naJehovha, "Zvakabatirwa neljipiti, nezvakashambadzirwa neItiopia, navaShabhea, ivo varume varefu, zvichauya kwauri, zvichava zvako; vachakutevera, vachauya vakasungwa namatare, vachapfugama pamberi pako, vachikunyengera, vachiti, `Zvirokwazvo Mwari uri pakati pako, hakuna mumwe, hakuna mumwe Mwari.' "
\v 15 Zvirokwazvo, muri Mwari anovanda, imi Mwari waIsiraeri, Muponesi.
\v 16 Ivo vose vachanyadziswa vave nenyadzi; vaiti vezvifananidzo vac
\s dziswa pamwechete.
\p
\v 17 Asi vaIsiraeri vachaponeswa naJehovha noruponeso rusingaperi; hamunganyadziswi kana kuva nenyadzi kusvikira panguva dzisingaperi.
\p
\v 18 Nokuti zvanzi naJehovha akasika denga rose, iye Mwari akaumba nyika nokuiita, akaisimbisa akasaisika kuti rive dongo, asi akaiumba kuti igarwe, zvanzi naye, "Ndini Jehovha, hakuna mumwe.
\v 19 Handina kutaura pakavanda, panzvimbo yenyika yerima; handina kuti kurudzi rwaJakobho, `Nditsvakei pasina,' ini Jehovha, ndinotaura zvakarurama, ndinoparidza zvechokwadi.
\p
\v 20 "Unganai, muuye; swederai pamwechete, imi makapukunyuka kumarudzi; vanotakura matanda iri mifananidzo yavo yakavezwa havana ruzivo, ivo vanonyengetera mwari asingagoni kuponesa.
\v 21 Paridzai, muzvibudise; zvirokwazvo, ngavarangane pamwechete, vachiti, `Ndiani akazviratidza izvi kubvira panguva yekare-kare? Ndiani akazviparidza pakutanga?' Handizini Jehovha here? Hakuna mumwe Mwari kunze kwangu, Mwari akarurama noMuponesi, hakuna mumwe kunze kwag:Li,
\v 22 Tuttai
\p ndiri muponeswe, imi mativi ose enyika; nokuti ndini Mwari, hakuna mumwe.
\v 23 Ndakapika neni ndimene, shoko rabuda mumuromo mangu nokururatna, haringadzoki, kuti mabvi ose achandipfugamira,
\p marimi ose achapika neni.
\v 24 Zvanzi pamusoro pangu, `Kururama nesimba zviri muna Jehovha bedzi; vanhu vachauya kwaari, vose vakanga vamutsamwira vachanyadziswa.
\v 25 Rudzi rwose rwaIsiraeri rucharuramisirwa muna Jehovha, nokuzvirumbidza maari.' " §-
\s Vamwari vaBhabhironi naMwari
\s wahiraeri vanofananidzwa
\p
\v 46
\v 1 Bheri anowira pasi, Nebho anokotama; zvifananidzo zvavo zviri
\p pamusoro pezvipfuwo nemombe, zvinhu zvamaitakura zvakaitwa mutoro, wakatakudzwa zvipfuwo zvaneta.
\v 2 Vanokotama, vanowira pasi pamwechete, vakakoniwa kurwira mutoro, asi ivo vamene vakatapwa.
\p
\v 3 "Nditeererei, imi imba yaJakobho, navakasara veimba yaIsiraeri, vakatakurwa neni kubva pakuberekwa kwavo, vakasimudzwa kubva pachizvaro;
\v 4 kusvikira makwegura, ndini iye, ndichakutakurai kusvikira vhudzi renyu rachena; ini ndakakuitai, ndichakutakurai, zvirokwazvo ndichakusimudzai, nokukurwirai.
\v 5 Muchandifananidza naniko, nokundienzanisa nani, nokunditi ndakaita sani, wandingafanana naye?
\v 6 Ivo vanodurura ndarama pahombodo, nokuyera sirivha nechiyero, vanoripira mupfuri wendarama, iye ndokuita mwari nayo; zvino vopfugama, nokunamata.
\v 7 Vanochikwidza pamapfudzi, vanochitakura, ndokuchigadzika panzvimbo yacho, icho ndokumira; hachibvi panzvimbo yacho, zvirokwazvo, kunyange munhu akadana kwachiri, hachigoni kupindura, kana kumuponesa pakutambudzika kwake.
\p
\v 8 "Rangarirai chinhu ichi, muve varume, fungaizve chinhu ichi, imi vadariki.
\v 9 Rangarirai zvinhu zvapfuura zvakare; nokuti ndini Mwari, hakuna mumwe, ndini Mwari, hakuna akafanana neni;
\v 10 iye anoparidza kubva pakutanga izvo zvichaitika pakupedzisira, nokubva panguva yekare-kare zvinhu zvichigere kuitwa, ndichiti, `Zvandakarayira zvichamira, ndichaita zvose zvandinoda;' lindinodana gondo ribve kumabvazuva, muWk% waAdAmyilka `&()N e, \(\my \ka kure; zvirokwazvo, ndakataura, ndichazviuyisawo, ndakazvitema, ndichazviitawo.
\v 12 Nditeererei, imi mune mwoyo mikukutu, imi muri kure nokururama;
\v 13 Ndichaswededza kururama kwangu,
\s yomudondo; anosima mupaini, mvura inonaya ndokuukurisa.
\p
\v 15 Zvino dzava huni dzomunhu, anotora dzimwe ndokudziya nadzo; zvirokwazvo, anobatidza moto nadzo, ndokubika chingwa; zvirokwazvo, anoveza mwari, ndokumunamata; anoita mufanananidzo wakavezwa, ndokuupfugamira.
\v 16 Rumwe rutivi rwawo anopisa nomoto, norumwe rutivi anogocha nyama, anoidya nyama, nokuguta zvirokwazvo, anozvidziyisa, ndokuti, "Haiwa, ndadziya, ndaona moto."
\v 17 Nezvakasara anoita mwari, iwo mufananidzo wake wakavezwa; anoupfugamira, nokuunamata, nokunyengetera kwauri, achiti, "Ndirwirei, nokuti ndimi mwari wangu."
\p
\v 18 Havazivi, uye havarangariri, nokuti wakanamira meso avo, kuti varege kuona, nemwoyo yavo, kuti varege kunzwisisa.
\v 19 Hakuna anorangarira, hakuna ruzivo kana njere dzinoti, "Ndapisa rumwe rutivi rwawo mumoto, zvirokwazvo, ndabika chingwa pamazimbe awo; ndagocha nyama ndikaidya; zvino ndingaita chinonyangadza nezvakasara zvawo here? Ndingapfugamira danda romuti here?"
\v 20 Anozvigutisa namadota; mwoyo wakanyengerwa wamutsausa, haagoni kusunungura mwoyo wake, kana kuti, "Hakuna nhema muruoko rwangu rworudyi here?"
\p
\v 21 Funga zvinhu izvi, iwe Jakobho, naIsiraeri, nokuti ndiwe muranda wangu; ndakakuumba, uri muranda wangu; haiwa Isiraeri, haungakanganikwi neni.
\p
\v 22 Ndakadzima kudarika kwako, segore gobvu, nezvivi zvako segore; dzokera kwandiri, nokuti ndakakudzikinura.
\p
\v 23 Imba, iwe denga rose, nokuti Jehovha akaita izvozvo; danidzirai, mativi ezasi enyika; imbai zvikuru imi makomo, iwe dondo, nomuti mumwe nomumwe urimo; nokuti Jehovha akadzikinura Jakobho, achazvirumbidza muna Isiraeri.
\p
\v 24 Zvanzi naJehovha, Mudzikinuri wako, akakuumba kubva pachizvaro, "Ndini Jehovha, anoita zvinhu zvose, anotatamura denga rose iye oga, anotambanudza nyika (ndiani waiva neni?)
\v 25 Iye anoparadza zviratidzo zvavane
\s nhema, anopengesa vauki, anodzosa vachenjeri, achishandura zivo yavo uye upenzi.
\p
\v 26 "Iye anosimbisa shoko romuranda wake, anoita zvakarayirirwa nenhume dzake; iye anoti pamusoro peJerusaremu, `Richagarwa navanhu,' napamusoro pamaguta aJudha, `Achavakwa, ini ndichamutsa matongo awo;'
\v 27 iye anoti kumvura yakadzika, `Chipwa, uye ndichapwisa nzizi dzako,'
\v 28 iye anoti pamusoro paKoreshi, `Ndiye mufudzi wangu, achaita zvose zvinondifadza,' kana achiti pamusoro peJerusaremu `Richavakwa,' uye pamusoro petemberi, `Nheyo dzako dzichateyiwa.'
